
### get token

POST http://localhost:8080/api/public/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}


### admin: create user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "newpassword",
  "roles": ["USER"]
}

### admin: change user password
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/newuser/password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newPassword": "changedPassword123"
}

### admin: grant role
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/newuser/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### admin: revoke role
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/newuser/roles/ADMIN
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### admin: set user active flag
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/newuser/active?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### admin: list active users (paged)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/active?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### admin: delete user
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/newuser
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### tests: list all (paged)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tests?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### tests: get by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tests/{{testId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### tests: create (admin)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Midterm Exam",
  "semesterSubjectId": "{{semesterSubjectId}}",
  "classId": "{{classId}}"
}

### tests: update (admin)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tests/{{testId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Midterm Exam",
  "semesterSubjectId": "{{semesterSubjectId}}",
  "classId": "{{classId}}"
}

### tests: delete (admin)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tests/{{testId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json


### grades: semester aggregation (admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/grades/semester?semesterId={{semesterId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### grades: semester aggregation for one student (admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/grades/semester?semesterId={{semesterId}}&studentId={{studentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
